                                                  Māryām</title>
                  <note>Incomplete at the end. Between <locus target="#179v #180r" facs="182">fols. 179v, 180r</locus> there is a missing folio</note>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.1"><locus from="168r" facs="170">Fols 168r and following</locus><title>Monday</title></msItem>
